After downloading and unpacking, select all ttf files, right click, install&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;iv-install-windows-terminal-preview&#34;&gt;IV. Install Windows Terminal Preview&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Search for Windows Terminal Preview in the Windows App Store and install it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;v-install-the-new-version-of-powershell&#34;&gt;V. Install the new version of Powershell&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just go all the way to the next step, it is recommended to install to Powershell folder in D drive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;vi-install-oh-my-posh&#34;&gt;VI. Install oh-my-posh&lt;/h1&gt;
